metadata.description:
Original lumen print is produced on black and white photographic paper using photographic chemicals in combination with a variety of resists and by the means of exposure to sunlight and UV light source.

This digital version of the analog original is 2075 x 3000, 300ppi pixels in size, and is offered for non-commercial use in a limited edition of 10.
JPEG/Signed original print
